# [[maple]] tree
#: {{syn|ja|蛙手|tr=kaerude}}
# a [[color]] [[scheme]] for {{ja-r|襲|かさね|lit=[[layering]]|[[layered]] [[kimono]]}}, with light [[chartreuse]] layers on the outside and [[yellow]] or [[vermillion]] on the inside
# a kind of {{ja-r|家%紋|か%もん|{{w|mon (emblem)|family crest}}}}, featuring a maple-leaf design
# {{lb|ja|sort=かえで|term of endearment}} a [[child]]'s hand {{qualifier|from the resemblance in shape between a hand with [[splayed]] fingers and a maple leaf}}

